#### About India Ink

This report on India from the journalists of The New York Times and a pool of
talented writers in India and beyond provides unbiased, authoritative
reporting on the country and its place in the world. India Ink also strives to
be a virtual meeting point for discussion of this complex, fast-changing
democracy – its politics, economy, culture and everyday life.

